responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "18114D2F407460F2809D3FA2F9FEF205", "Come and dance three sisters of Sephillion. Dance the dance and wish for me. Edyria, warrior most proud, What wonders do you wish to see? I wish to be a champion, a power most feared. Like a gladiator in an arena, I want to revel in the applause of many!")
